00:59:22.304 --> 00:59:23.599
People love to talk.

00:59:24.463 --> 00:59:25.539
They love to tell you.

00:59:26.021 --> 00:59:28.340
And you know, at the end of the meeting, they don't even remember what you say.

00:59:28.440 --> 00:59:28.838
But you know what?

00:59:29.284 --> 00:59:30.219
I like that guy.

00:59:31.342 --> 00:59:32.719
Because they feel good about it.

00:59:33.039 --> 00:59:38.159
Because some people actually, they try to talk, you know, to their partner, to their business partner.

00:59:38.340 --> 00:59:39.239
Nobody listens to them.

00:59:39.905 --> 00:59:40.440
They're frustrated.

00:59:41.563 --> 00:59:43.579
