00:59:43.679 --> 00:59:45.460
And if you get the money along the way, it's even better.

00:59:46.083 --> 00:59:46.938
That's what we do sometimes.

00:59:47.400 --> 00:59:51.159
By the way, when we started the call with the Brazilian guy, just to connect with the guy.

00:59:51.260 --> 00:59:52.320
Because I just watched Sena.

00:59:52.844 --> 00:59:53.659
