Have you been to Al Bahari?

01:07:01.804 --> 01:07:02.179
Have you seen?

01:07:02.461 --> 01:07:03.159
What are you looking for?

01:07:03.380 --> 01:07:04.500
Oh, I'm looking for a basement.

01:07:05.242 --> 01:07:06.860
I'm looking for an entertainment room.

01:07:07.059 --> 01:07:09.010
I'm looking for a longevity area.

01:07:10.900 --> 01:07:12.780
I'm looking, how many children do you have?

01:07:13.427 --> 01:07:14.159
I have five kids.

01:07:14.581 --> 01:07:15.900
Do you receive a lot of guests?

01:07:16.019 --> 01:07:16.980
Yes, I love to entertain.

01:07:17.382 --> 01:07:19.079
I receive ministries and stuff.

01:07:19.260 --> 01:07:20.119
That's why I need a bedroom.

01:07:20.842 --> 01:07:21.519
Okay, you know what?

01:07:21.659 --> 01:07:25.219
The best value for money right now is Al Bahari.

01:07:26.601 --> 01:07:30.398
You get 13,000 square foot for like 75.

01:07:31.222 --> 01:07:32.860
It's very good value for money.

01:07:33.201 --> 01:07:35.500
And by the way, if I may, why not considering Al Bahari?

01:07:35.659 --> 01:07:36.659
You work mostly from home.

01:07:37.764 --> 01:07:38.559
Have you been to Al Bahari?

01:07:38.699 --> 01:07:42.199
Do you know that it's like two or three degrees less than because of the trees and all this?

01:07:42.340 --> 01:07:42.840
Have you been there?

