No.

01:36:31.220 --> 01:36:33.060
You have the teaser, which is one pager.

01:36:33.421 --> 01:36:33.673
Uh-huh.

01:36:34.104 --> 01:36:35.020
You have the video.

01:36:35.801 --> 01:36:38.859
And you have also always a little text that I sent.

01:36:40.087 --> 01:36:40.759
We will send it to you.

01:36:41.100 --> 01:36:41.960
