01:36:52.399 --> 01:36:53.798
Just something very simple like this.

01:36:54.641 --> 01:36:56.520
Because some people will not open the teaser.

01:36:58.002 --> 01:36:59.779
Some people will just look at the video.

01:37:00.301 --> 01:37:01.199
