02:28:41.780 --> 02:28:44.356
Yes, but actually we've done more than 29% in average.

02:28:45.501 --> 02:28:47.391
But that's why we're telling you that's what we've done.

02:28:47.412 --> 02:28:48.799
We're not going to hide what we're doing.

02:28:49.402 --> 02:28:50.927
The priority return is 15%.

02:28:51.630 --> 02:28:52.153
Execution.

02:28:52.213 --> 02:28:53.076
Who manage the project?

02:28:53.096 --> 02:28:53.819
You have the whole team.

02:28:54.861 --> 02:28:55.725
What if it doesn't sell?

02:28:55.986 --> 02:28:56.709
We can still rent.

02:28:57.050 --> 02:28:58.156
We can still reduce the price.

02:28:58.217 --> 02:28:58.879
We can still decide.

02:28:59.059 --> 02:29:00.390
Anyway, we're not taking the decision.

02:29:00.411 --> 02:29:01.459
The investor take the decision.

02:29:04.520 --> 02:29:04.881
Downside.

02:29:04.961 --> 02:29:05.363
Timing.

02:29:05.626 --> 02:29:06.067
Why now?

02:29:06.328 --> 02:29:07.736
I mean, right now?

02:29:08.257 --> 02:29:08.659
You know, guys.

02:29:10.484 --> 02:29:11.417
Let's talk about right now.

02:29:15.301 --> 02:29:17.719
What we're noticing is all of the European investors,

02:29:17.820 --> 02:29:19.079
they're more on the freezing mode.

02:29:19.720 --> 02:29:24.020
But we have Indian investors, Russian investors, local investors.

02:29:24.604 --> 02:29:25.479
Some of them, they are here.

02:29:25.559 --> 02:29:26.534
They keep on investing.

02:29:27.120 --> 02:29:29.540
So those are more the people that understand the market.

02:29:29.980 --> 02:29:33.020
And the luxury market as well, there is always people that want to live in it.

02:29:33.622 --> 02:29:35.700
So the people that are like, yeah, I want to wait,

02:29:36.341 --> 02:29:38.079
just tell them, it's fine.

02:29:38.163 --> 02:29:38.559
Let us know.

02:29:38.700 --> 02:29:41.100
But when the market is going to pick up, how much would you like to invest?

02:29:41.260 --> 02:29:44.120
And you always go back to that question to try to take commitment.

02:29:44.941 --> 02:29:48.020
And you can also ask, where do you currently invest your money right now?

02:29:49.244 --> 02:29:50.180
And you get curious, you know.

02:29:51.884 --> 02:29:53.079
And some people, they tell you Europe,

02:29:53.140 --> 02:29:55.299
so you can sell green blue properties in France as well.

02:29:57.282 --> 02:29:58.559
And allocation, can I start small?

02:29:58.700 --> 02:30:00.477
Yes, they can start with as little as $10,000.

02:30:01.751 --> 02:30:01.940
You know.

02:30:02.886 --> 02:30:03.360
I'm done, guys.

02:30:03.500 --> 02:30:04.834
Otherwise, I'm going to overwhelm you.

02:30:06.540 --> 02:30:07.020
Thank you.

02:30:07.040 --> 02:30:08.120
This is finished.

02:30:09.108 --> 02:30:09.600
Any questions?

02:30:11.797 --> 02:30:11.860
No?

02:30:13.869 --> 02:30:14.299
Thank you, guys.

02:30:15.120 --> 02:30:16.139
Igor, are you still with us?

02:30:16.381 --> 02:30:17.340
You gave up, right?

02:30:18.305 --> 02:30:19.379
You mostly gave up anyway.

02:30:20.061 --> 02:30:20.559
No, you're here.

02:30:22.667 --> 02:30:23.239
You're in the pool?

02:30:24.808 --> 02:30:25.439
We cannot hear you.

02:30:26.626 --> 02:30:27.058
Okay, guys.

02:30:28.511 --> 02:30:28.738
You good?

02:30:30.066 --> 02:30:30.478
See you, Igor.

02:30:31.646 --> 02:30:32.040
We're good, man.

02:30:34.440 --> 02:30:38.120
Guys, for those of you that want to go and have some lunch,

02:30:38.402 --> 02:30:39.020
it's going to be on me.

02:30:39.602 --> 02:30:40.559
You can enjoy a free lunch.

02:30:44.002 --> 02:30:45.297
We're going to go to KFC, of course.

02:30:45.680 --> 02:30:46.019
No, I'm joking.

02:30:46.781 --> 02:30:47.840
We're going to go to Jumeirah Island.

02:30:48.021 --> 02:30:48.319
It's nearby.

02:30:48.780 --> 02:30:50.540
And then we go to Albarari because we need to run.

02:30:51.184 --> 02:30:52.040
But I'm here for you guys.

02:30:52.262 --> 02:30:52.759
Was it helpful?

02:30:53.120 --> 02:30:53.332
Yes.

02:30:54.212 --> 02:30:54.639
Was it helpful?

02:30:55.211 --> 02:30:55.360
Really?

02:30:56.586 --> 02:30:56.940
Helpful?

02:30:57.501 --> 02:30:58.658
Jessica, we're on a break.

02:31:00.882 --> 02:31:03.780
I've got to go, but I will speak to you soon

02:31:04.802 --> 02:31:06.576
