02:31:09.582 --> 02:31:12.899
Because broker in the U.S. is you own your own company.

02:31:13.399 --> 02:31:14.278
But broker here is...

02:31:14.801 --> 02:31:15.091
You can...

02:31:16.513 --> 02:31:16.719
See you?

02:31:16.860 --> 02:31:17.659
Yeah, see you soon.

02:31:18.243 --> 02:31:18.707
Thank you, Ryan.

02:31:21.843 --> 02:31:22.591
I'm fluent in Mandarin.

02:31:24.083 --> 02:31:25.879
I can speak, write, read Chinese.
